name: Player One
description:
Hi.. thank you for visiting my third drop.

Player one.
this is all a matter of perspective, as a human being who is endowed with the sensitivity of intellegence, of course, also burdened with destiny that sharpens that blessing. How heavy or light it is is not an excuse but a way of seeing and looking for solutions and responding to the situation is very important. All decisions are not only for the best but also for consequences so enjoy those choices and tread slowly. because the landscape is shrouded in white fog.
